data.name: InfoGameDescription_Label.Text
data.value:
• Use the mouse to move the pot and catch the healthy food that is dropping
• There are 3 levels in which food drops more and significantly faster
• At level 3 the food randomly switches location once it reaches the middle. Quick reflexes!

data.name: InfoRecipesDescription_Label.Text
data.value:
• Use the coins in your account to purchase healthy recipes from our shop
• Once certain recipe is bought, you can check it's recipe at anytime without spending more of your coins
• Make sure you follow the recipe correctly and eat healthy
